step_data.thought: Looking at the current state of the page, I can see that we're already on a product edit page for a Yoga Mat product. The product has been successfully saved, as indicated by the message 'You saved the product.' visible on the page. The form shows all the information we've entered: Product Name (Yoga Mat), SKU (Yoga MatYM-001), Price (29.99), Quantity (100), and Weight (2.5 lbs). The product is enabled, set as 'In Stock', and has 'Taxable Goods' selected for Tax Class. Since the goal was to add a new Yoga Mat product to the inventory, and we've successfully done that and received confirmation that the product was saved, our task is complete. I should inform the user of the successful completion.
